OL,3,CDriver found with suspected knife
OL,4,Cinjuries after crash
OL,6,FA man in his twenties has been
OL,7,Farrested, after the driver of a
OL,8,Fcrashed vehicle in Doncaster was found
OL,9,Fwith serious injuries believed to have
OL,10,Fbeen caused by a knife.
OL,12,FIn the early hours of Wednesday 4
OL,13,FMarch, South Yorkshire Police were
OL,14,Fcalled to Hexthorpe Road by the
OL,15,Fambulance service after a single
OL,16,Fvehicle collision shortly after 5.30am.
OL,18,FThe driver was found with serious
OL,19,Finjuries and was taken to hospital. He
OL,20,Fremains in a serious condition which
OL,21,Fis not thought to be life-threatening.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
