OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772651488
OL,3,CDriver found with suspected knife
OL,4,Cinjuries after crash
OL,6,FPolice believe the serious injuries
OL,7,Fwere caused by a knife.
OL,9,FInvestigations have established the
OL,10,Finjuries happened in an earlier
OL,11,Fincident at a property on the same
OL,12,Fstreet.
OL,14,FA man, 20, has been arrested on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of assault and remains in
OL,16,Fcustody.
OL,18,FRoad closures are still in place
OL,19,Faround St James's Bridge.
